    "title": "符號加法覆面算",
    "questionText": "在右側所示的加式中，記號 ◇、♡ 與 ▽ 分別代表三個互不相同的數碼。請問 ◇♡▽ 代表的三位數是什麼？",
    "questionSvg": "<div class='bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-6 rounded-xl flex justify-center'><svg width='200' height='150' viewBox='0 0 200 150'><g font-size='36' font-family='sans-serif' font-weight='900' fill='#1e293b'><text x='70' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#0ea5e9'>◇</text><text x='120' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444'>♡</text><text x='170' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#f59e0b'>▽</text><text x='20' y='90' text-anchor='middle'>+</text><text x='70' y='90' text-anchor='middle' fill='#0ea5e9'>◇</text><text x='120' y='90' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444'>♡</text><text x='170' y='90' text-anchor='middle' fill='#f59e0b'>▽</text><line x1='10' y1='105' x2='190' y2='105' stroke='#1e293b' stroke-width='4'/><text x='70' y='145' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444'>♡</text><text x='120' y='145' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444'>♡</text><text x='170' y='145' text-anchor='middle'>4</text></g></svg></div>",
    "finalAnswer": "497",
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "步驟一：觀察十位數特徵",
        "content": "十位數的算式為 ♡ + ♡ (+進位) = ♡。<br/>唯一能在加倍後（加上進位 1）字尾還是保留自己的數碼，只有 <strong class='text-[#D4AF37]'>♡ = 9</strong>。<br/>(9 + 9 + 1 = 19，留下 9 並進位 1)。"
      },
      {
        "title": "步驟二：還原算式求解",
        "content": "既然 ♡ = 9，代表結果的和為 <strong class='text-[#D4AF37]'>994</strong>。<br/>也就是說：◇9▽ + ◇9▽ = 994。<br/>將和除以 2 即可求出原數：994 ÷ 2 = <strong class='text-[#D4AF37] bg-[#D4AF37]/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded'>497</strong>。"
      }
    ]
  },
