  "Q30": {
    "title": "整數的非重複拆分 (雙解法教學)",
    "questionText": "總共有多少種不同的方法將 100 寫成三個「不同」正整數之和？(不考慮順序，如 34+5+61 與 61+34+5 視為相同方法)。",
    "questionSvg": "<div class='bg-slate-100 border border-slate-300 p-6 rounded-xl text-center'><p class='text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2'>a + b + c = 100</p><p class='text-[#D4AF37] font-bold mb-4'>條件：1 ≤ a &lt; b &lt; c</p><svg width='240' height='40' viewBox='0 0 240 40' class='mx-auto'><circle cx='20' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/><circle cx='50' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/><line x1='75' y1='5' x2='75' y2='35' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='4'/><circle cx='100' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/><circle cx='130' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/><circle cx='160' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/><line x1='185' y1='5' x2='185' y2='35' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='4'/><circle cx='210' cy='20' r='10' fill='#94a3b8'/></svg><div class='mt-4 flex justify-center gap-2 flex-wrap'><span class='px-3 py-1 bg-[#0ea5e9]/10 text-[#0ea5e9] rounded-md text-sm font-bold border border-[#0ea5e9]/20'>解法一：高中隔板法</span><span class='px-3 py-1 bg-[#ef4444]/10 text-[#ef4444] rounded-md text-sm font-bold border border-[#ef4444]/20'>解法二：國中列舉法</span></div></div>",
    "finalAnswer": "784",
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "解法一：高中隔板法",
        "content": "將 100 拆成 3 份，等同在 99 個空隙插 2 個隔板，共 C(99, 2) = <strong class='text-[#D4AF37]'>4851</strong> 種。<br/>扣除兩數相同的情況 (49×3=147種)，三數皆不同的排列法有 4851 - 147 = 4704 種。<br/>因不考慮順序，需除以 3! (6種)：4704 ÷ 6 = <strong class='text-[#D4AF37]'>784</strong>。"
      },
      {
