        "content": "強制排序 1 ≤ a &lt; b &lt; c 避免重複。<br/>若 a=1, b+c=99 ➔ b可為2~49，共 <strong class='text-[#0ea5e9]'>48</strong> 種<br/>若 a=2, b+c=98 ➔ b可為3~48，共 <strong class='text-[#ef4444]'>46</strong> 種<br/>若 a=3, b+c=97 ➔ b可為4~48，共 <strong class='text-[#0ea5e9]'>45</strong> 種<br/>...依此類推至 a=32，共 <strong class='text-[#ef4444]'>1</strong> 種。"
      },
      {
        "title": "等差數列求和",
        "content": "分兩組等差數列求和：<br/>奇數列：48 + 45 + ... + 3 = <strong class='text-[#0ea5e9]'>408</strong><br/>偶數列：46 + 43 + ... + 1 = <strong class='text-[#ef4444]'>376</strong><br/>總和：408 + 376 = <strong class='text-[#D4AF37] bg-[#D4AF37]/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded'>784</strong> 種方法。"
      }
    ]
  }
